### Variables — set for your deployment
@base = http://localhost:3000
@token = paste-jwt-or-use-cookie-from-browser

### Boss creates foreman / brigadir (session cookie from browser login)
POST {{base}}/api/users/foreman
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Site Foreman",
  "email": "foreman@company.com",
  "password": "secret12"
}

### Login (sets HttpOnly cookie on same origin)
POST {{base}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "boss@demo.local",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### Current user
GET {{base}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Projects (boss: full finances; foreman: assigned only, no prices)
GET {{base}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create project (boss)
POST {{base}}/api/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Warehouse renovation",
  "location": "Industrial zone",
  "totalPrice": 48000,
  "advancePayment": true,
  "advanceAmount": 10000,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Attendance upsert
POST {{base}}/api/attendance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "workerId": "WORKER_ID",
  "date": "2026-05-03",
  "present": true,
  "hours": 8
}

### Move inventory to project (deducts stock)
POST {{base}}/api/inventory/move
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "inventoryItemId": "ITEM_ID",
  "projectId": "PROJECT_ID",
  "quantity": 10,
  "note": "Delivered to site"
}

### Expenses (boss only)
POST {{base}}/api/finance/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 320,
  "date": "2026-05-03",
  "category": "MATERIALS",
  "projectId": null,
  "description": "Fuel"
}

### Monthly report (boss only)
GET {{base}}/api/reports/monthly?year=2026&month=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Custom P&L by range (boss only)
POST {{base}}/api/reports/custom
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "2026-05-01",
  "to": "2026-05-31",
  "projectId": "OPTIONAL_PROJECT_ID"
}

### Cron — monthly snapshot (set CRON_SECRET in env)
GET {{base}}/api/cron/monthly-report
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CRON_SECRET
